  "detailed_description": "Monochro is an action-platformer game about a person who explores the colorful world.<br><br>Use the unique weapons carried by balloons and the air-dash to reach the end of the world.<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397530/extras/a4df145148c8bc11776607daca558eb1.poster.avif?t=1602427442\" width=704 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397530/extras/a4df145148c8bc11776607daca558eb1.webm?t=1602427442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397530/extras/a4df145148c8bc11776607daca558eb1.mp4?t=1602427442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Key Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unique Weapons</strong><br>Annihilate all enemies with weapons, sword, shotgun, missile and so on.<br><br></li><li><strong>Rank Up</strong><br>Players will obtain EXP in battle and gain player rank. When the player rank up, they get an upgrade or a heart.<br><br></li><li><strong>Randomly Generated World</strong><br>Each level is procedurally generated each time.</li></ul><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397530/extras/29bc5a286787ba6bd69d4616bd9a35fd.avif?t=1602427442\" width=572 height=64 /></span><br><br><strong>Update log</strong><br><br>v1.1.1<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Changed some effects<br></li><li>Adjusted wall kick<br></li><li>(Japanese text only) Changed the text of thunderbolt</li></ul><br>v1.1.0<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Added easy mode</li></ul><br>v1.0.2<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Added thunderbolt effect<br></li><li>Fixed bug of XInput controller</li></ul><br>v1.0.1 <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Improved some weapons<br></li><li>Changed weapon icon graphics<br></li><li>Adjusted balloons<br></li><li>Adjusted player attack movement</li></ul>",
